{"tid":193542,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！G伏新作企劃中！","createTime":"2017-04-09T11:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T14:03:50.000Z","uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22eadeaaa315fb8ef197aa4da55156ccc9a0833d","tid":193542,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:21:40.000Z","msg":"深度作品你識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「ガンダム Gのレコンギスタ」新プロジェクト企画進行中！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.gundam.info/uploads/image/20160601193934-97371.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gundam.info%2Fuploads%2Fimage%2F20160601193934-97371.jpg&h=75e63497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nイタリア・ローマで開催中のアニメ・マンガイベント「Romics」では、4月8日（土）に『ガンダム Gのレコンギスタ』の上映会とともに、スペシャルゲストとして招待された富野由悠季総監督のファンミーティングが行われた。<br />\n<br />\n会場では、現地のアニメファンとの交流を深めるとともに、『ガンダム Gのレコンギスタ』の新プロジェクトが企画進行中であることも語られた。<br />\n<br />\n新プロジェクトについては情報が入り次第お届けしていくので、今後の続報をお楽しみに。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gundam.info/topic/17864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gundam.info%2Ftopic%2F17864&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b5e0bc9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gundam.info/topic/17864</a>"},{"pid":"ee349350164643a4eb133ea1f6ba5edcf9211df4","tid":193542,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"超越第一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c961275102fedd6ea742401787f0b5bd8afec911","tid":193542,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:55:52.000Z","msg":"富野都回曬塘,收皮吧啦"},{"pid":"c1c720fad48bd2b99cd32eb73d0b01a63c9f1b73","tid":193542,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:56:54.000Z","msg":"富野又出山了"},{"pid":"50f2199192eeb1b86fa6e62d35bef6cdc501abcb","tid":193542,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:22:27.000Z","msg":"富